{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"iarc_rating_id","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/iarc_rating_id","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"\n<ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/background_color\">background_color</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/categories\">categories</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/description\">description</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/dir\">dir</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/display\">display</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/display_override\">display_override</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/iarc_rating_id\">iarc_rating_id</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/icons\">icons</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/lang\">lang</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/name\">name</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/orientation\">orientation</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/prefer_related_applications\">prefer_related_applications</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/protocol_handlers\">protocol_handlers</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/related_applications\">related_applications</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/scope\">scope</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/screenshots\">screenshots</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/short_name\">short_name</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/shortcuts\">shortcuts</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/start_url\">start_url</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/theme_color\">theme_color</a></li></ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"properties\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">型</th>\n      <td>`String`</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">必須</th>\n      <td>いいえ</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n<p><em><code>iarc_rating_id</code></em> メンバーは、ウェブアプリケーションの <a href=\"https://www.globalratings.com/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">International Age Rating Coalition (IARC)</a> 認証コードを表す文字列です。これは、このウェブアプリケーションがどの年齢向きであるかを示すために使うためのものです。</p>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>Note:</strong> 流通する製品が同じである限り、同じコードを複数の参加店舗で共有することができます（つまり、異なる店舗で全く異なるコードパスを提供しない）。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: json notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token property\">\"iarc_rating_id\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"e84b072d-71b3-4d3e-86ae-31a8ce4e53b7\"</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"仕様書","id":"仕様書","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/manifest-app-info/#iarc_rating_id-member","title":"Web App Manifest - Application Information"}],"query":"html.manifest.iarc_rating_id"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"ブラウザーの互換性","isH3":false,"query":"html.manifest.iarc_rating_id","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/iarc_rating_id/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"関連情報","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.globalratings.com/how-iarc-works.aspx\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">IARC が動作する仕組み</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.globalratings.com/for-developers.aspx\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">開発者がゲームやアプリで IARC の格付けを受ける方法</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"例","id":"例"},{"text":"仕様書","id":"仕様書"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"ブラウザーの互換性"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"関連情報"}],"summary":"iarc_rating_id メンバーは、ウェブアプリケーションの International Age Rating Coalition (IARC) 認証コードを表す文字列です。これは、このウェブアプリケーションがどの年齢向きであるかを示すために使うためのものです。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"iarc_rating_id","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"iarc_rating_id","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/manifest/iarc_rating_id"